Title: TOWARDS A COMPLETE DETECTION/CORRECTION SYSTEM  
Author: J. COURTIN, D. DUJARDIN, I. KOWARSKI, D. GENTHIAL, V.L. DE LIMA 
Keyword: morphological parsing and generation, similarity keys, phonetics, syntactic parsing, syntactic verification, unification, concordancy correction  
Address: BP 53X, F-38041 Grenoble CEDEX, FRANCE  
Affiliation: Laboratoire de Gnie Informatique, IMAG-Campus  
